performanceinspector-portlet-link: The name of the link in the portlet menu, when the inspector is activated.
performanceinspector-dialog-title: The heading in the dialog that displayes the inspector.
performanceinspector-dialog-summary:
The name of the summary field for all collected data for the inspector
{{Identical|Summary}}
performanceinspector-dialog-cancel:
The text of the cancel button in the dialog
{{Identical|Cancel}}
performanceinspector-modules-summary-tot: The total weight of all modules, displayed in the summary section
performanceinspector-modules-name:
The name of the module part of the dialog
{{Identical|Module}}
performanceinspector-modules-label: The label of the module part of the dialog
performanceinspector-modules-css-title:
The heading for the CSS section
{{Identical|CSS}}
performanceinspector-modules-css-column-:
The column name for modules in the CSS section
{{Identical|Module}}
The column name for allSelectors in the CSS section
The column name for matchedselectors in the CSS section
The column name for percentMatched in the CSS section
performanceinspector-modules-localstorag: The heading for the Local storage section
This is displayed if local storage is disabled

The number of hits in local storage
{{Identical|Hit}}

The number of misses in local storage
{{Identical|Miss}}

The number of modules that was expired in local storage
{{Identical|Expired}}
The total size of modules in local storage
performanceinspector-imagesize-name: The name of the page size of the dialog
performanceinspector-imagesize-label: The label of the page size of the dialog
performanceinspector-imagesize-column-im:
Name of the column displaying the image name
{{Identical|Name}}
performanceinspector-imagesize-column-si:
The name of the column displaying the size of the image
{{Identical|Size}}
performanceinspector-imagesize-column-im:
The name of the column displaying extra information about the images.
{{Identical|Extra}}
performanceinspector-imagesize-too-big:
Information displayed in the extra column if the image is too big.
{{Identical|Warning}}
performanceinspector-imagesize-descripti: Description of the image section, displayed before the table of images.
performanceinspector-imagesize-warning-d: Explain how the wanring system for images work: Images over 1 mb will be flagged as too big.
performanceinspector-modules-summary-ima: Information from the images displaying the summary information from the image objects.
performanceinspector-newpp-summary: The summary from the the parser report.
performanceinspector-newpp-name: The name of the NewPP report of the dialog
performanceinspector-newpp-label: The label of the NewPP report part of the dialog
performanceinspector-newpp-column-name: The name of the column header for a metric of the NewPP report
performanceinspector-newpp-column-value: The name of the column header for the value of the NewPP report
performanceinspector-newpp-value-and-lim: Displaying value and the limit for a metric. Metric is the first parameter and limit the second one.
performanceinspector-newpp-template-time: The column header name for the template name
The column header name for time spent in percentage
The column header name for time spent
The column header name for number of calls per template
performanceinspector-newpp-parsed-by: The text explaining the hostname of the server that parsed the page metric
performanceinspector-newpp-cached-time: The text explaining the when the page was cached metric
performanceinspector-newpp-parsed-ttl: The text explaining when the cache will expire metric
performanceinspector-newpp-dynamic-conte: The text explaining the if the page dynamic content metric
performanceinspector-newpp-cputime: The text explaining the CPU time spent generating the page metric
performanceinspector-newpp-walltime: The text explaining the time spent generating the page metric
performanceinspector-newpp-ppvisitednode: The text explaining the number of nodes visited by the preprocessor metric
performanceinspector-newpp-ppgeneratedno: The text explaining the number of nodes generated by the preprocessor metric
performanceinspector-newpp-postexpandinc: The text explaining the post-expand include size metric
performanceinspector-newpp-templateargum: The text explaining the template argument size metric
performanceinspector-newpp-expansiondept: The text explaining the highest expansion depth metric
performanceinspector-newpp-expensivefunc: The text explaining the expensive parser function count metric
performanceinspector-newpp-timingprofile: Header name for the timing profile part
performanceinspector-newpp-scribunto: Header name for scribunto report part
performanceinspector-newpp-cachereport: Header name for the cache report
